Invocation Name: inner witness
des:
Listen to this timeless story of a Peace Tribe called the Sakshi Tribe. Grab you camera to witness life through your open eyes and start an inner journey with the Sakshi in you? Are you a part of this tribe, that has known and understood nature for millennia, are you a Sakshi, as you take a deep breath and join in this story, you discover your inner self and your inner journey, the Sakshi and the 'I', the digital life and the natural.
